dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is George Russell. May I have your name, please?
Hi George, my name is Melissa Barnes.
Nice to meet you, Melissa. Could you please provide me with your policy number and date of birth for verification purposes?
Sure, my policy number is six five zero three two and my date of birth is March twenty seventh, nineteen eighty-five.
Thank you, Melissa. One last thing, can you confirm the make and model of your vehicle you wish to add to your policy?
Of course, it's a black two zero one five Toyota Camry.
Thank you for providing that information, Melissa. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
No, that's all for now. Thank you, George.
You're welcome, Melissa. If you have any more questions in the future, feel free to reach out. Have a great day!
